            {
              "text": "Anna points to a fruit shop that sell fresh fruit for a good price.",
              "audioStart": 13.863,
              "audioEnd": 17.413
            },
            {
              "text": "As they walk, a loud noise from a near shop draws their attention.",
              "audioStart": 18.275,
              "audioEnd": 21.837
            },
            {
              "text": "In that moment, people push forward and Emily finds herself away from Anna near the main entrance.",
              "audioStart": 22.7,
              "audioEnd": 27.837
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Emily feels a bit afraid because she can not see Anna among the many people.",
              "audioStart": 28.7,
              "audioEnd": 32.587
            },
            {
              "text": "She looks around, tries to remember the route they took, and hopes to hear Anna call her name.",
              "audioStart": 33.45,
              "audioEnd": 38.263
            },
            {
              "text": "A kind woman who walk near notices Emily worry and ask if she need any help.",
              "audioStart": 39.125,
              "audioEnd": 43.388
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily says she is away from Anna and can not know the way back to the fruit shop.",
              "audioStart": 44.25,
              "audioEnd": 48.062
            },
            {
              "text": "The woman says she will guide Emily to the information office that is near the main entrance.",
              "audioStart": 48.925,
              "audioEnd": 53.3
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily thank the woman and follow her through the big market toward the bright sign that mark the office.",
              "audioStart": 54.163,
              "audioEnd": 59.025
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The information office is run by a kind employee who say people well and offer good map.",
              "audioStart": 59.888,
              "audioEnd": 64.45
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily ask is heard by staff and a clear map is given to her quickly.",
              "audioStart": 65.312,
