            {
              "text": "The map show the route that lead back to the fruit shop where Anna may wait for her friend.",
              "audioStart": 73.162,
              "audioEnd": 77.338
            },
            {
              "text": "If Emily had follow the signs early, she would have find Anna soon and avoid the worry.",
              "audioStart": 78.2,
              "audioEnd": 82.638
            },
            {
              "text": "The kind woman tell Emily that calm and safe will help her find the way without further trouble.",
              "audioStart": 83.5,
              "audioEnd": 88.287
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily look, feels a bit more sure, and thank the woman for the clear help.",
              "audioStart": 89.15,
              "audioEnd": 93.237
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Emily walk toward the fruit shop but a small group of people block the small street near the water.",
              "audioStart": 94.1,
              "audioEnd": 98.862
            },
            {
              "text": "She ask a shop owner if there is another route and the shop owner say yes, there is a side street.",
              "audioStart": 99.725,
              "audioEnd": 104.725
            },
            {
              "text": "If she had take the left street early, she could have avoid the block and save time.",
              "audioStart": 105.588,
              "audioEnd": 109.625
            },
            {
              "text": "The map show that the side street go around the people and lead right to the fruit shop entrance.",
              "audioStart": 110.487,
              "audioEnd": 115.125
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily thank the shop owner and move fast along the side street, follow the signs on the map.",
